class Solution {
    /**
    Given ana rray  arr o f  integ ers, find  the minimum number o f elements that     need to be chan ged to make the array  palindromic.  A palindromicarray is a n  array that
    is read thesa me backwards and forwa rds. In one change, you can change one element to anyother  element.

